#description "This mod pack by AetherNomad focuses on the Early Ages and the ancient mediterranean world; it includes the following:
- 13 EA mod nations with enhanced mutual compatibility: Thalamanth v1.30, Triliax v1.25, Nephelococcygia v1.33, Isphenople v1.24, Arcadeia v1.23, Nabatem v1.24, Karanaac v1.26, Cyanautha v1.18, Zun v1.18, U v1.12, Bethel She'em v1.05 and, in Hellenika-specific versions, Knoss (by Zonk) and Makedon (by Mirokan);
